						               													<description>For decades the Blanco family has run the town of San Luis on the New Mexico border. So, they didn&amp;rsquo;t take to kindly to John Bannon when he rode into town and made himself the sheriff. Soon the silver mines, saloons and stage-coach were all working for him. Tensions between the Blancos and Bannon were boiling over when a quiet stranger with a wicked gun rode into town. Who will win control of San Luis?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The mini-campaign is loosely based on the film &amp;quot;A Fistful of Dollars&amp;quot; and is structured in quick &amp;ldquo;acts&amp;rdquo; that could be played in a single evening. &amp;#10;Both sides face decisions that allow for a great deal of replay value and let the players write their own story in the West....&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players choose their own adventure with one side picking the scenario and the other choosing the set up.  &amp;#10;There are a possible 27 different battles that can be played.&amp;#10;The mini-campaign will consist of three of these gunfights.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;RUTHLESS, a complete set of western gunfight rules, is also included!  &amp;#10;This booklet has everything you need to play!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
